text: Harry James Souttar (born 22 October 1996) is a Scottish-born Australian soccer player. He plays for Leicester City in the EFL Championship and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Fleetwood Town F.C. players Category:Scottish footballers Category:Sportspeople from Aberdeen Category:Leicester City F.C. players Category:Premier League players Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
